Title: The Panty Sniffer
Plot: Catherine and Detective Vartann are thrown together in a hotel room for 24 hours as they stake out a duo making drugs in the room next door. Meanwhile, Nick and Langston work a case that involves a fetish which has become big business in Vegas.
GuestStars: Curtis Armstrong, Eddie McClintock, Matt Barr, Jackson Davis, Ian Anthony Dale, Alex Carter, Archie Kao, Melissa Ponzio, Charles Divins, Nicole Garza
